text: Lin Yung-hsi (born 26 March 1979) is a Taiwanese gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Taiwan Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Medalists at the 2002 Asian Games
